cross: Phalaenopsis Joyce Stewart x Phalaenopsis lindenii

measurements.description: Fifteen flowers and 23 buds well-distributed on an upright branched inflorescence of 22cm; sepals and petals white striped pink, petals lightly flushed pink; lip white, side lobes striped pink, midlobe darker pink, central callus bright yellow; column flushed dark pink, anther cap white; substance medium; texture diamond dust.
